Job Description
Fresh Graduates with fluency in English or candidates having less experience in Call Center may apply for "Customer Sales Representative' or "Senior Sales Executive" post respectively. We are equal opportunity provider. Girls are encouraged to applyBeside the basic salary we provide splendid package of bonuses and incentives. JOB DUTIES: No field work! We deal with US customers using automatic dialing system and telecommunication technologies. Persuade customers to buy services by following a prepared sales talk providing the necessary information and price quotation.
Work individually and with team to achieve the required targets.
Work in accordance to company’s rules and regulation to maintain a save and healthy working environment.
